"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-romantic-william-boyd-fiction-review-scenes-of-a-century-fc855e30?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">“浪漫”评论：一个世纪的场景</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-romantic-william-boyd-fiction-review-scenes-of-a-century-fc855e30"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-833545?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">G. Dagli Orti/布里奇曼图片社</span></div></div></div><p></p>威廉·博伊德的全景小说讲述了拿破仑的最后一战、斯里兰卡的恐怖以及与拜伦勋爵的谈话。<em>布鲁克·艾伦评论</em><p></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-romantic-william-boyd-fiction-review-scenes-of-a-century-fc855e30?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/finding-w-h-hudson-review-the-enigmatic-birdman-bcff07e1?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《寻找 WH 哈德森》评论：神秘的鸟人</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
